Anne Charleston https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Anne_Charleston 0 Anne Charleston (born 30 December 1942 in Melbourne) is an Australian actress best known for playing the character of Madge Bishop in the Australian soap opera Neighbours and Lily Butterfield in British soap Emmerdale.
